  <text>
      <body>
        
     
      <div xml:id="Broken"> 
              <interpGrp type="poembox">
                <interp ana="#form" type="sonnet"></interp>
                <interp ana="#tone" type="other"></interp>
                <interp ana="#topic" type="death"></interp>
              </interpGrp>
             <lg> 
               <l>We went in to see</l>
               <l>TO see the broken line </l> 
               <l>Though good people we once may have been</l>
               <l>can we still make that claim from now on in forward time?</l>
               <l>Men, boys and animals lives</l>
               <l>Perished defending a scrap of ground </l>
               <l>A solemn quiet now we see with our own eyes </l>
               <l>Where smoke and sharp lead reigned hell from the sky murdering the ground</l>
               <l>Doubts too painful to bear</l>
               <l>live in our minds constantly</l>
               <l>a tear for love, a smile or a care</l>
               <l>do we still have the right to feel any humanity?</l>
               <l>We enter the Treanch to see</l>
               <l>To see the broken line. </l>
               
